
& piloting-quad
 
 >> Help: Piloting-Quad (Piloting Skills)
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Used for piloting rolls while in a quad unit (such as walking through water,
 staggering from damage, etc.).
 
 To see specifics on quad mechs, type 'help quad'.
 
 For a detailed look at this skill, see our online documentation:
 docs.btmux.com/index.php/Skills%2C_Stats%2C_Attributes%2C_and_Advantages
 
